===Noun===
'''[[Gregorian]] [[calendar]]'''
# The [[calendar]], currently used in the [[western]] [[world]], named after [[Pope]] Gregory XIII, devised to halt the slow drift of the [[Vernal equinox]] earlier in the [[year]].

